.TH "Math.expm1" "JS" "2023-06-02" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.hy
.SH Synopsis
.PP
The \f[B]\f[VB]Math.expm1()\f[B]\f[R] static method returns e raised to
the power of a number, subtracted by 1.
That is
